Package: xiacf
Type: Package
Title: Quantifying Nonlinear Dependence via Xi-ACF and IAAFT Surrogates
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yasunori Watanabe
Authors@R: person(given = "Yasunori", family = "Watanabe",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "watanabe.yasunori@outlook.com")
Maintainer: Yasunori Watanabe <watanabe.yasunori@outlook.com>
Description: Implements the Xi-ACF framework for detecting deterministic chaos 
    in financial time series. Includes high-performance C++ implementations of 
    Chatterjee's Xi correlation coefficient and the IAAFT (Iterated Amplitude 
    Adjusted Fourier Transform) surrogate algorithm.
